Hereâ€™s a complete and working Maven configuration using Jakarta JAXB 4.0.4, compatible with Java 17+, and supporting:
	â€¢	.xsd schemas (e.g., PEPPOL UBL)
	â€¢	.xjb binding files (e.g., Lombok annotations)
